Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:17.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片天空下和{\rOPCH}你{\rOPJP}一起{\rOPCH}飞{\rOPJP}翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:17.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空へ君と走り出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:24.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿{\rOPCH}为你实现{\rOPJP}所有的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:24.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願い事全部叶えてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:41.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\rOPCH}这{\rOPJP}个和那个的麻{\rOPCH}烦{\rOPJP}不断涌来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:41.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれやこれやと押し寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾几{\rOPCH}时{\rOPJP}同平常生活{\rOPCH}说{\rOPJP}Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつのまにか日常をGoodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あのてこのて 猫でだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぐるぐる回る空へHELLO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:53.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能稀里糊{\rOPCH}涂{\rOPJP}下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:53.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うかうかしてられない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:56.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急がなきやいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:02:02.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君への思い妄想なんだか 空回りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不走{\rOPCH}运{\rOPJP}的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ついてないことも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:13.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也{\rOPCH}许总{\rOPJP}会有一天也能成{\rOPCH}为{\rOPJP}很好的机遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:13.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大きなチヤンスになるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:20.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有天{\rOPCH}见{\rOPJP}到{\rOPCH}你{\rOPJP}的笑{\rOPCH}脸{\rOPJP}一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:20.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の笑顔が見れたならきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:24.88,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,にゃんこがなるって　前を向けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.55,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まさににゃんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:32.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能有一天这双手能牵到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:32.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつかこの手届きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:38.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够把所有的愿望都为你实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:38.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願いを当然ぶっかなえてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市内的三丁目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标记是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天一定要努力不迷路的完成邮递工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿咧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…为啥不和我打招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我要是打扰你大清早潜逃的话怪不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么呢 这么多行李
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊 今天开始就要去修学旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶~~真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 它刚刚喵喵的叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 那啥 是打的喷嚏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 再不走就错过集合时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我闪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了给我带点土特产啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7只猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我到天黑HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh High 终于到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所憧憬的地方 行事多多的城市 京都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌舞多多 美食多多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对 先要巴士的导游姐姐给搞定掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就完成了委托了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢 帮大忙了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 在这里真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份恩情 没齿难忘 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门时一下子闯过来的时候 我还以为会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官人 听闻你要去京都旅行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请务必顺道带上这位{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我跟你一起归乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 总之现在就是久违了的自由之身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要借这个机会和水野一起去温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂同学 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士就要开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 常盘高中二年三班的同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位到来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好的享受四天三夜的京都之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会充满热情的去享受的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 大家做的好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这里就是跳落自杀的好舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排名第一的 清水寺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野 喂 很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了咋办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就先跳下去看看呗 润平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你干什么啊 危险 危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害怕么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你…你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂同学好机灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物是形容看上去很废的人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有小猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂润平大大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂大 你在附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道我的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿咧 高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经三天没有吃东西了呢 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你们从哪里打听到我的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}哥在街上说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己对猫过敏却奋不顾身的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非那家伙 在全京都境内都在传我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是京都御所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都御所从镰仓时代中期开始直到明治时代初期为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晕 开什么国际玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天满宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 学业之神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是个白痴 所以就买个护身符带…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,润平不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我的主人一定会高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金阁寺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 说「奶酪」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙安寺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看镜头（实在不知道是哪国语= =）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍无可忍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二条城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿咧 高坂同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他说他身体不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车内休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 他没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs27}(这个人是川口导演的好朋友，渡边慎一，搞笑片的有名画家,本集作画导演）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸头可是很蓬松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能丢卒保车了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这里是J
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}（J就是润平じゅんぺい罗马字首字母）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快回信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手机号码是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那啥 我有事拜托你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在年轻人之间流行的游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记录~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 还没好吗 好重啊小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘————
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵 喵 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边忙不开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧抓住他 赶紧让他闭嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:07:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我也不是很清楚啊 {\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}哥的住所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27}（书名注目= =脸红注目*= =*）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在京都遇到了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会暂时的在熟人这边避风头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土特产的话我可是要正宗的银鳕西京渍或者锦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你丫个头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预~备~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 中井小姐 晚上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你花痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被有女友的家伙说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂同学 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不舒服的话要我帮你联系老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野好温柔啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了 一之濑前辈的老家就在这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 老家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈其实是京都人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲都住在这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,润平个混蛋 在那边给我装纯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办 这份呼之欲出的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈酱 头发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊啊啊 好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27}（手的位置明显是故意的）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行 最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快找找啊 一定会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面可就是女温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煞风景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一群小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人必须要珍惜啊 可不能当东西看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃太 你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里 从这里能看的很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's show time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要第一个拜见天国之景色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拜佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没怎么烧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度的话看不出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个枫…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚刚开始加奈酱就好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了 蒸汽太浓看不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 赶紧换人啊晃太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别看了啊 stop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我住手啊 特别是水…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 原来你下榻这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 阿嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢 多谢你的午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢 那我就给你个独家消息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这边的缝看的话能看的更清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忍耐啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被恶魔的耳语所蛊惑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能对那么纯洁无暇温柔的水野进行如此不知廉耻的偷窥行为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只是稍微看一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且不能轻易拒绝猫的好意啊 不然有可能会加深诅咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是代价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高…高…高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们听一下我这不值一提的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是色胆包天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 高笨那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要多嚣张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈酱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 照这个样子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不会和那个家伙再有什么发展了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天咱们去岚山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也邀请高笨一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让他好好的补偿今天这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…高坂同学是不是有点可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢砸我~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩的话我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}（板子上：深刻反省）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂 你又在反省吗喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这也是过敏诅咒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌了 修学旅行什么的最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祗园精舍钟声响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嘣 诉说世事本无常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得真好 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我美丽的家乡京都哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 虽然不是我本意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴彦 我跟你商量之后决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英子的说 {\rNAGI}雛{\rDefault}子的说 过来过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哥哥真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祗园的日常小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四条的丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锦最棒的茶泡饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大原的和小物工房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\rNAGI}叡{\rDefault}山的豆腐皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 还有……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物清单我已经给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈为了这一天　早就备好了私房钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节衣缩食就是为了今天的土产？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家自由活动 下午5点集合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是迟到的话就一个一个查你们的行李哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晃太 我们快点走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在和谁发短信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得这么干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么老实就交代了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要告诉你们一个很好的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在网上查了下 说京都最好的约会地点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鸭川河边的长椅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到处都是情侣 气氛100分！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛……100分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 夜景真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 水野 还是你更迷人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 润平 今天跟我们一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多肯定更有意思 是吧 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨尊指示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 昨天的事 今天让你好好补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是丸子最好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住吉 你到底要吃多少才……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能顶嘴 这个偷窥boy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 有船啊 船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 再这样吃下去的话 买礼物的钱就……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是那个传说中被诅咒的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危机又增加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 肚子也填饱了 我们到周围逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 住吉 我……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 要走了吗 真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个势头……也许不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 高坂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍的很不错是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是修学旅行最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 这一片好像有清单中的店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里 我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点离开这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 好个性 挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 润平 买下这……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我有点事……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你们先回去吧 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 润平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂 同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 那家伙搞什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真让人担心啊 润平是个路痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭之前不赶回去的话 我们也要负连带责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,good
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢你了 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你想起来点什么没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如主人的名字啦 家的标志之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 阿咧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫 小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高坂 不好意思 我们放心不下就跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事啊 我们不知道所以就跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪啊 小{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}…你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yes……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是那个小猫的爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,润平 难道……你是在照顾迷路的小猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊 真是太感谢你了 连儿子也受你照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为报答 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉是叫我们跟着他们走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 偶然猜对的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂……等……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑组 的……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本部！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 以防万一大家拼上命去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真是巧遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault} 还有行踪不明的阿{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么难多说这些家伙要在京都避风头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都的熟人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 你在这边做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然就是这家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是{\rNAGI}凪{\rDefault}前辈京都的老家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 每年这个时候是家族的大会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇遇啊 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的妻子 辛迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你来 请不要客气 高坂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有妻子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}是个很好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再敢给我搞外遇的话我就揍你肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了 在小孩子面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外遇是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 它暂时住在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一听说小{\rNAGI}柾{\rDefault}平安降生 就再也呆不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那个女人已经有很多孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 夫妇吵架猫也不愿管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}（小知识：这里是应该是{\rNAGI}“夫婦喧嘩は犬も食わぬ”{\rDefault}\N这里把犬改成猫了。意思就是两口子吵架）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有猫食就吃点零食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 你还真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你也眼花缭乱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同追两兔 不 三兔一兔不得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 你还是这么迟钝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了{\rNAGI}凪{\rDefault}前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 回学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 偶然还真是惊人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到在这么大的京都里……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对不住可爱的后辈 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和高坂也许是命中注定要在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了 太美好了 my light destiny 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂润平 果然是个不可大意的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 吃的好饱啊 这样就吃不下旅馆的饭菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看 夕阳好漂亮 看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情……情侣遍地……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是很不错的回忆啊 嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能和水野……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能和润平……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人来到这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好了 已经这个时候了 会被老师骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是……是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水……水野……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……这个给你……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次的 回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（黑道新娘）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在电影周边店里买的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你是否喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁哥~ 谢谢 我一直在找这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高笨 我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是请你大吃一顿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级新干线之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的猫猫小课堂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.47,0:23:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑组 大会仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有请 组长大驾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之女儿将在这群男人中 寻找女婿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要找黑道上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.56,0:23:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑组的大会是为了让小姐找女婿而办的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都西阵的称念寺被称为“猫寺”非常有名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺内还有被称为“猫松”的高大松树哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下集猫愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.26,0:23:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真慢啊 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎……回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么会在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还特地给你带来了有困难的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.21,0:23:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有困难的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我想学会抓麻雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集猫愿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8只猫 炎的私人教授跑者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.85,0:24:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生 应该对女生的内衣感兴趣吧
