Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:25.25,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}思い描く未来には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:30.04,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}两人的笑脸 除此以外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:30.04,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}二人の笑{\rEDJP}顔{\rEDCH} それ以外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:31.79,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}什么也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:31.79,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}もう{\rEDJP}見{\rEDCH}えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:35.03,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这会是如此寂寞的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:35.03,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}こんなに切ない{\rEDJP}気{\rEDCH}持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:38.25,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就算这心情被你觉察到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:38.25,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\rEDJP}気{\rEDCH}ついてくれなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:41.53,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也只在心中默默许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:41.53,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}心にそっと{\rEDJP}願{\rEDCH}うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.73,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}希望明天愿望一定实现！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.73,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日になれば叶うはず！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:48.10,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}擦肩而过的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:48.10,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}すれ{\rEDJP}違{\rEDCH}った瞬{\rEDJP}間{\rEDCH}に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:51.19,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}对我舒展开你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:51.19,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑いかけてくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:54.54,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这就能让我激动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:54.54,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}それだけて胸が{\rEDJP}熱{\rEDCH}い
